00:36:28.370 --> 00:36:30.320 position:56%
I didn't realize that at that point.

00:36:30.320 --> 00:36:32.430
So I stopped writing because
I was like, you know what?

00:36:32.430 --> 00:36:33.730
This is a sign that I'm not meant

00:36:33.730 --> 00:36:36.370
to be a writer, and
maybe I should stop.

00:36:36.370 --> 00:36:38.710
And maybe adults don't
write fantasy.

00:36:38.710 --> 00:36:40.700
Like that's not a thing
that adults like.

00:36:40.700 --> 00:36:42.000
I should be serious.

00:36:42.000 --> 00:36:43.300
I should grow up.

00:36:43.300 --> 00:36:46.670
I should age out of this and
stop chasing this fantasy.

00:36:46.670 --> 00:36:48.070
You know, no pun intended.

00:36:48.070 --> 00:36:52.060
So I stopped writing for two
years, and it took me going

00:36:52.060 --> 00:36:54.190
into the videogame
industry, actually,

00:36:54.190 --> 00:36:55.710
to convince me to start
writing again.

00:36:55.710 --> 00:36:58.360
Because that was the first
time in my life where I was

00:36:58.360 --> 00:37:02.530
with other young people who love
games, who loved the creative arts

00:37:02.530 --> 00:37:03.920
and weren't ashamed of it.

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:06.940
You know, love what they were
doing, that was the moment

00:37:06.940 --> 00:37:08.430
where I was like, oh, okay.

00:37:08.430 --> 00:37:11.820
It's okay to love these things, and
I'm going to write no matter what.

00:37:11.820 --> 00:37:13.500
Because if you're a
writer, you know, whether

00:37:13.500 --> 00:37:16.730
or not you get published, it's
a part of you, it doesn't matter

00:37:16.730 --> 00:37:18.100
if you're published or unpublished.

00:37:18.100 --> 00:37:19.400
You're a writer.

00:37:19.400 --> 00:37:20.700
We're all writers.

00:37:20.700 --> 00:37:22.000
If you write, you're a writer.

00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:24.250
So with that in mind, I
started writing again,

00:37:24.250 --> 00:37:25.550
because I was like, you know what?

00:37:25.550 --> 00:37:26.850
Who cares?

00:37:26.850 --> 00:37:28.150
I'm just having fun.

00:37:28.150 --> 00:37:29.450 position:56%
You know, this is what I want to do.

00:37:29.450 --> 00:37:30.750
So I'm going to do it.

00:37:30.750 --> 00:37:32.120
And I wrote another book
which didn't get published,

00:37:32.120 --> 00:37:35.500
and because of, you know, the
rejections that I had gotten before

00:37:35.500 --> 00:37:38.540
and this new revelation,
I was able to keep going

00:37:38.540 --> 00:37:42.640
after this fourth kept
getting rejected.

00:37:42.640 --> 00:37:43.940
I was like, okay, you know what?

00:37:43.940 --> 00:37:45.240
It's fine.

00:37:45.240 --> 00:37:46.830
I'll make a fort out of
the rejection letters.

00:37:46.830 --> 00:37:49.630 position:56%
And then I wrote this book, and that
was Legend, and it got published.

00:37:49.630 --> 00:37:54.540 position:56%
So yeah, you keep going because you
never know what's on the other side.

